thread.title: Peta Purdon
thread.title_full: Temple & Webster reviewed by Peta Purdon

author: Peta Purdon
title: Peta Purdon
text: The Selena bed frame and Loft bedside table were delivered separately. Both were despatched promptly and the product quality was excellent. Unfortunately, the table was damaged in transit. The follow up was expeditious and very satisfactory and it was very reassuring to deal with such professional and courteous people.
